      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I've kept up with all the maintenance, so it's ready for its next adventure. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
