    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS. This specimen has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the drivetrain. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a functional variable M differential lock for superior power distribution. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup that delivers precise feedback through the steering rack. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the performance envelope remains undiminished, offering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
