    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use like light stone chips on the front valence. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the premium upholstery remains firm and comfortable, with no significant wear on the bolsters. All technological features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a documented history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Outfitted with a set of high-quality tires with ample tread remaining, this car is truly turn-key and ready for its next journey. It offers a refined driving experience that reflects its careful ownership, making it an exceptional choice for a buyer seeking reliability and value.",
